---
title: Mexican Fiesta Chicken & Corn Tacos with Slaw & Spring Onion
description: Sit back and watch the fireworks display of flavour burst through these chicken tacos. They’re packed with colourful veggies like
corn and carrot and the chicken is exploding with our Mexican Fiesta spices. To cool off, drizzle over some creamy mayo!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
